### Promotion CRUD API Tests

### Get all promotions
GET {{host}}/api/v1/promotions

### Get promotions with pagination
GET {{host}}/api/v1/promotions?page=1&pageSize=5

### Search promotions
GET {{host}}/api/v1/promotions?search=SUMMER

### Get promotion by ID
GET {{host}}/api/v1/promotions/1

### Get promotion by promo code
GET {{host}}/api/v1/promotions/code/SUMMER2024

### Get active promotions
GET {{host}}/api/v1/promotions/active

### Create new promotion
POST {{host}}/api/v1/promotions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "promoCode": "SUMMER2024",
  "description": "Summer sale promotion",
  "discountType": "percent",
  "discountValue": 20.00,
  "startDate": "2024-06-01T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2024-08-31T23:59:59Z",
  "minOrderAmount": 100.00,
  "usageLimit": 100,
  "status": "active"
}

### Create fixed discount promotion
POST {{host}}/api/v1/promotions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "promoCode": "SAVE50",
  "description": "Save $50 on orders over $200",
  "discountType": "fixed",
  "discountValue": 50.00,
  "startDate": "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2024-12-31T23:59:59Z",
  "minOrderAmount": 200.00,
  "usageLimit": 0,
  "status": "active"
}

### Update promotion
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/promotions/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "promoCode": "SUMMER2024",
  "description": "Updated summer sale promotion",
  "discountType": "percent",
  "discountValue": 25.00,
  "startDate": "2024-06-01T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2024-08-31T23:59:59Z",
  "minOrderAmount": 150.00,
  "usageLimit": 200,
  "status": "active"
}

### Validate promotion
POST {{host}}/api/v1/promotions/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "promoCode": "SUMMER2024",
  "orderAmount": 250.00
}

### Delete promotion
DELETE {{host}}/api/v1/promotions/1
